<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. &quot;Lalpa tawh cheng khawm di'n!&quot;
 Ahi ahi, Amen;
 Thihna pat hinna a um,
 Manthai theihlohna chuh;
 Zie lei taksa ahin,
 Amah beiin ka vak;
 Zan bei zelin, ka naih deuh deuh,
 Nicheng in In ka naih.

[V2]
 In ka naih, In ka naih,
 Nicheng in In ka naih.

[V3]
 2. Ka Pa In van sangah,
 Ka thagau in a naih;
 Ginna mitin ka gal muh hi,
 Sana kawtkhak a lang;
 Ka thagau a chau hi,
 Ka lunggulh gam tung di'n;
 Mi thiengthote luoh ding In van,
 Chunglam Jerusalem.

[V4]
 3. Meipi hung zing mahleh,
 Lungtupna chau mahleh;
 Noah vakhu bangin ka leng,
 Tuilien, huihpi lakah;
 Meipi a kithiel tai,
 Huihpi, tuilien a hai;
 Ka lungthim lawpin, a kipak,
 Lungmuonna chu ka nei.

[V5]
 4. Zingkal leh nitak in,
 Sun leh zan, bangtik inle;
 Van lapawl ngaihnawp um ka zai,
 Lei chung pauchuuom beita;
 Zie thawkitna thu chuh,
 Zie zawhna la gi chuh;
 &quot;Lalpa tawh kumsawt a um ding,
 A hi, a hi, Amen.&quot;</lyrics>
<title>FOR EVER WITH THE LORD</title>
<hymn_number>180</hymn_number>
</song>